# Resend API key for the contact form (server-side only, NEVER exposed to the browser).
# 1. Create a free account at https://resend.com and generate an API key.
# 2. Add it as RESEND_API_KEY in the Vercel project Environment Variables (Production + Preview).
# 3. For local dev with `vercel dev`, copy this file to `.env` and paste the key below.
# The contact form posts to /api/contact (api/contact.ts), which sends mail via Resend
# to mlsatogo.club@gmail.com. This key is secret — keep it out of source control.
RESEND_API_KEY=
